# Placeholder files for Nako pack

Create these files with your Nako character content:

- `agent/IDENTITY.md` - Character identity card
- `agent/SOUL.md` - Personality and values
- `agent/HEARTBEAT.md` - Heartbeat message templates
- `agent/MEMORY.md` - Initial memory template
- `agent/USER.md` - User profile template
- `agent/AGENTS.md` - Main system prompt
- `agent/custom.md` - Custom layer (preserved on upgrade)

- `skills/voice/SKILL.md` - Voice skill
- `skills/vision/SKILL.md` - Vision skill
- `skills/hearing/SKILL.md` - Hearing skill
- `skills/selfie/SKILL.md` - Selfie skill
- `skills/dokidoki/SKILL.md` - Doki-doki skill
- `skills/memory/SKILL.md` - Memory skill

- `config/model-map.yaml` - Model mapping
- `config/providers-preset.json` - Provider presets
